Occupy Atlanta | Protesters vow to continue to be in park
By Christian Boone and Jeremiah McWilliams
The Atlanta Journal-Constitution


Occupy Atlanta protesters vowed Wednesday to continue to be in Woodruff Park even beneath threat of arrest.


